summary: Now that Phil is asking us for questions for a Q & A, I hope we will all remain respectful and only ask appropriate, polite and...
body:
Now that Phil is asking us for questions for a Q & A, I hope we will all remain respectful and only ask appropriate, polite and inoffensive questions.

Don’t ruin the experience for someone else by misusing the opportunity and being rude. This is not the place nor the time for it.

Also, it is not the time to ask about the hiatus or the theory they are quitting youtube. Despite some of us ranting the explanation they gave us wasn’t good enough, they’ve already talked about it, gave us a reason for the hiatus and said they’re not quitting. Let it go.
